<h1>Igor Stravinsky</h1>
<ul>

	<li><blockquote cite="/t/2510">
	<q>The twelve notes in each octave and the varieties of rhythm offer me opportunities that all of human genius will never exhaust.</q>
	<cite><a href="/t/2510">Igor Stravinsky</a></cite>
</blockquote>

</li>

	<li><blockquote cite="/t/1884">
	<q>Too many pieces of music finish too long after the end.</q>
	<cite><a href="/t/1884">Igor Stravinsky</a></cite>
</blockquote>

</li>

	<li><blockquote cite="/t/1749">
	<q>Art is the opposite of chaos. Art is organized chaos.</q>
	<cite><a href="/t/1749">Igor Stravinsky</a></cite>
</blockquote>

</li>

	<li><blockquote cite="/t/545">
	<q>Too many pieces of music finish too long after the end.</q>
